Author: juwo
Content: I disagree. From my blog post, "I recently dissolved the advisor group. Advisors are a fixture of startups. Advice is nice, but I much prefer effort - because Talk is Easy but Effort shows Commitment."\nFor advisors, look to books by Kawasaki, Paul Graham etc.\nI would rather get a good team.
